@using FluentUI.Demo.Shared.Pages.Calendar.Examples

<h1>Calendar</h1>

<p>
    <code>&lt;FluentCalendar&gt;</code> wraps the <code>&lt;fluent-calendar&gt;</code> element, a web component implementation of a month calendar display leveraging the Fluent UI design system.
    It allows for setting a range of selected and/or disabled dates and can handle a click on a day event (if not <code>Readonly</code>)
</p>

